9 An Act relating to retirement; amending 62 O.S. 2021,
Section 3103, as last amended by Section 2, Chapter
10 361, O.S.L. 2024 (62 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 3103),
which relates to the Oklahoma Pension Legislation
11 Actuarial Analysis Act; modifying terms; amending 47
O.S. 2021, Sections 2-304, as amended by Section 2,
12 Chapter 45, O.S.L. 2025, and 2-305, as last amended
by Section 9, Chapter 151, O.S.L. 2023 (47 O.S. Supp.
13 2025, Sections 2-304 and 2-305), which relate to the
Oklahoma Law Enforcement Retirement System; modifying
14 employer contribution; modifying employee
contribution; modifying top base salary provisions;
15 modifying positions that receive certain benefit
computation; providing that certain provisions apply
16 to certain individuals; providing effective dates;
providing for contingent effective dates based on
17 outcome of approval of the emergency clause; and
declaring an emergency.
